        <h2>Dragons: Masters of the Skies</h2>
        
        <div class="creature">
            <img src="dragon_image_1.jpg" alt="Dragon Image 1">
            <div>
                <h3>Ember Wyrm</h3>
                <p>The Ember Wyrm is a fire-breathing dragon with scales that glow like molten lava. Known for their fiery tempers, they can raze entire cities with a single burst of flame. They prefer to dwell in volcanic regions, using the heat of the earth to replenish their energy.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="creature">
            <img src="dragon_image_2.jpg" alt="Dragon Image 2">
            <div>
                <h3>Frostmaw Dragon</h3>
                <p>The Frostmaw Dragon has the ability to breathe a deadly freezing mist, capable of freezing entire landscapes within seconds. Its icy breath can create devastating blizzards, and its appearance often heralds the coming of a new Ice Age.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="creature">
            <img src="dragon_image_3.jpg" alt="Dragon Image 3">
            <div>
                <h3>Stormwing Dragon</h3>
                <p>The Stormwing Dragon is known for its ability to control the weather. With its massive wings, it can summon violent storms and lightning strikes, using the skies as its personal weapon. Its thunderous roars can be heard for miles around.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="creature">
            <img src="dragon_image_4.jpg" alt="Dragon Image 4">
            <div>
                <h3>Void Drakon</h3>
                <p>These dragons are masters of the void, existing in both our world and the shadowy realms beyond. Their eyes glow with the power of the void, and they are capable of manipulating space itself, creating rifts that allow them to travel instantly from one location to another.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="creature">
            <img src="dragon_image_5.jpg" alt="Dragon Image 5">
            <div>
                <h3>Ironclaw Dragon</h3>
                <p>The Ironclaw Dragon is a formidable beast, with scales as hard as steel. It is often seen as the ultimate guardian of treasure hoards, using its massive claws to crush anyone daring to approach its domain. They have a reputation for being both intelligent and ruthless.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

