                <p>The Harbinger Swarm is a collective species of small, flying aliens that work together in perfect harmony. Individually, they are weak, but in a swarm, they are deadly. They can overwhelm entire cities in minutes, incapacitating anyone caught within their cloud of relentless, sharp appendages.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="creature">
