                <h3>Necron Lords</h3>
                <p>The Necron Lords are cybernetic alien beings that have transcended biology. Their metal bodies are impervious to most attacks, and they are often seen leading vast armies of reanimated soldiers. Their primary goal is to harvest Earth's resources for their own nefarious purposes.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

