        <h2>Survival: Humanity's Last Stand</h2>
        <p>Humanity's remnants live in scattered underground shelters and remote safehouses. The fight for survival is constant, as both dragons and aliens patrol the surface. Technology is all but lost, and every remaining survivor must rely on the knowledge passed down from the previous generation to stay hidden and resist the forces that have taken over.</p>
